p.k: Justin is on the hook to help out his new stepmom Julia at her little gathering. Unfortunately for him, this means putting on a ridiculous looking vest and regaling his stepmom's social club. Things were looking pretty stale until Olivia makes an appearance. She can't quite keep her eye off Justin once she sees the meat he's packing for an appetizer. After a risky encounter, Olivia and Julia can't help but take a moment. Reminiscing about old times certainly get Julia wet. She can't help herself getting a taste for old time's sake. When Justin bursts in wondering where they are, Olivia decides he's already got what it take to give these ladies what they crave!
